# 
# https://erct.adaptcentre.com/ontology#hasEvaluationMethod
<https://erct.adaptcentre.com/ontology#hasEvaluationMethod> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
