<https://erct.adaptcentre.com/ontology#hasEvaluationMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Facet property for evaluation design or methodology. Values should be IRIs of erct:EvaluationMethod concepts, for example individual randomization or stratified randomization. Multiple values are allowed when a trial reports mixed methods."@en .
